
From the following table, write a SQL query to compute the sum of the allotment amount of all departments. Return sum of the allotment amount.Programming

Sample table: emp_department

DPT_CODE DPT_NAME        DPT_ALLOTMENT
-------- --------------- -------------
      57 IT                      65000
      63 Finance                 15000
      47 HR                     240000
      27 RD                      55000
      89 QC                      75000

-- This query calculates the sum of 'dpt_allotment' from the 'emp_department' table.
SELECT SUM(dpt_allotment)
-- Specifies the table from which to retrieve the data (in this case, 'emp_department').
FROM emp_department;
